there is a photo.  Some lucky bus owner will be
getting it for the *low* price of $199 unless someone
gets to it first in the next 10 hours.   I have lots
of photos at http://photos.yahoo.com/j_griffin100
under the Eberspacher Folder.

Good luck with getting your bus warmed up!   
